# TESTING.md — E2E and keyboard/focus notes

**Authority:** [TESTING.md](TESTING.md) — Playwright setup, run commands, what suites cover (`game-core`, `board-keyboard`, `powerups`, `progression-stats`, `mobile-viewport`), manual keyboard/focus expectations.

## Before editing

- Read `TESTING.md` when adding or changing tests so new coverage matches documented intent (or extend the doc).

## After editing

- If you add a **new spec file**, change **global test setup** (e.g. server, reporters), or materially change **keyboard/focus behavior** documented for manual QA, **update `TESTING.md`**.
- Implementation details of mechanics belong in [GAME_SPEC.md](GAME_SPEC.md) or code; this file stays about **how we verify** and **manual checks**.
